\section{Multilingual Adaptation Methodology}
\label{sec:multilingual}

This section details how Al-Marjaa can be adapted to any language, demonstrating the process with concrete examples.

\subsection{Adaptation Process Overview}

Adapting Al-Marjaa to a new language involves four steps:

\begin{enumerate}
    \item \textbf{Keyword Definition:} Define native-language keywords
    \item \textbf{Syntax Configuration:} Adapt grammar rules
    \item \textbf{Localization:} Translate error messages and documentation
    \item \textbf{NLP Model:} Train or fine-tune a Vibe Coding model
\end{enumerate}

\subsection{Step 1: Keyword Definition}

Keywords must be chosen to resonate with native speakers while maintaining semantic consistency across languages.

\subsubsection{Keyword Selection Criteria}

\begin{enumerate}
    \item \textbf{Semantic Clarity:} The word should clearly convey its meaning
    \item \textbf{Linguistic Naturalness:} The word should feel natural in the language
    \item \textbf{Avoid Ambiguity:} The word should not have multiple conflicting meanings
    \item \textbf{Consistency:} Related keywords should use related terminology
\end{enumerate}

\subsubsection{Keyword Examples Across Languages}

\begin{longtable}{@{}llllll@{}}
\toprule
\textbf{Concept} & \textbf{Arabic} & \textbf{Chinese} & \textbf{Spanish} & \textbf{Russian} & \textbf{Hindi} \\
\midrule
\endfirsthead
\toprule
\textbf{Concept} & \textbf{Arabic} & \textbf{Chinese} & \textbf{Spanish} & \textbf{Russian} & \textbf{Hindi} \\
\midrule
\endhead
variable & متغير & 变量 & variable & переменная & चर \\
constant & ثابت & 常量 & constante & константа & स्थिर \\
function & دالة & 函数 & funcion & функция & फलन \\
class & صنف & 类 & clase & класс & वर्ग \\
if & إذا & 如果 & si & если & यदि \\
else & وإلا & 否则 & sino & иначе & अन्यथा \\
for each & لكل & 对于每个 & para_cada & для_каждого & प्रत्येक_के_लिए \\
while & بينما & 当 & mientras & пока & जब_तक \\
return & أرجع & 返回 & retornar & вернуть & लौटाएं \\
true & حق & 真 & verdad & истина & सत्य \\
false & باطل & 假 & falso & ложь & असत्य \\
null & فراغ & 空 & nulo & null & शून्य \\
new & جديد & 新 & nuevo & новый & नया \\
\bottomrule
\end{longtable}

\subsection{Step 2: Syntax Configuration}

Different languages may require different syntactic patterns:

\subsubsection{Statement Terminators}

\begin{lstlisting}[caption={Statement Terminator Variants}]
// Arabic: Arabic semicolon
متغير س = 10؛

// Chinese: Full-width semicolon
变量 x = 10；

// Western: Standard semicolon  
variable x = 10;

// Indic: Devanagari danda
चर x = 10।
\end{lstlisting}

\subsubsection{Block Delimiters}

\begin{lstlisting}[caption={Block Delimiter Options}]
// Brace style (universal)
دالة جمع(أ، ب) {
    أرجع أ + ب؛
}

// Keyword style (Python-like)
دالة جمع(أ، ب)
    أرجع أ + ب
نهاية

// Indentation style
دالة جمع(أ، ب):
    أرجع أ + ب
\end{lstlisting}

\subsection{Step 3: Vibe Coding for Any Language}

The Vibe Coding system enables natural language programming in any supported language:

\subsubsection{Arabic Example}

\begin{lstlisting}[caption={Arabic Vibe Coding}]
Input: "أنشئ متغير اسم يساوي أحمد"
Output: متغير اسم = "أحمد"؛

Input: "إذا كان العمر أكبر من 18 اطبع بالغ"
Output: إذا العمر > 18 { اطبع("بالغ")؛ }
\end{lstlisting}

\subsubsection{Chinese Example}

\begin{lstlisting}[caption={Chinese Vibe Coding}]
Input: "创建一个变量名字等于张三"
Output: 变量 名字 = "张三"；

Input: "如果年龄大于18就打印成年人"
Output: 如果 年龄 > 18 { 打印("成年人")； }
\end{lstlisting}

\subsubsection{Spanish Example}

\begin{lstlisting}[caption={Spanish Vibe Coding}]
Input: "crear variable nombre igual a Juan"
Output: variable nombre = "Juan";

Input: "si edad mayor que 18 imprimir adulto"
Output: si edad > 18 { imprimir("adulto"); }
\end{lstlisting}

\subsubsection{Russian Example}

\begin{lstlisting}[caption={Russian Vibe Coding}]
Input: "создать переменную имя равно Иван"
Output: переменная имя = "Иван";

Input: "если возраст больше 18 вывести взрослый"
Output: если возраст > 18 { вывести("взрослый"); }
\end{lstlisting}

